          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>RPPA Commercial Recreation Concessions Pilot Program Act of 2019</b></p> This bill directs the Department of the Interior to establish a pilot program that authorizes commercial recreation concessions on land patented or leased under the Recreation and Public Purposes Act. <p>Interior shall enter into at most 10 agreements with parties to whom such land has been patented or leased for the establishment of these concessions. </p> <p>A party to such an agreement may enter into agreements with third parties to establish such concessions.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-07-25T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
